request.description:
### Get Orphan Photos

This endpoint retrieves the photos of a specific orphan identified by the ID in the URL.

#### Request

- Method: GET

- URL: {{BASE_URL}}/api/orphans/682e138fb7bd42c55e5995e2/photos


#### Response

The response for this request is a JSON object with the following schema:

``` json
{
  "type": "object",
  "properties": {
    "status": {
      "type": "string"
    },
    "data": {
      "type": "object",
      "properties": {
        "photos": {
          "type": "array",
          "items": {
            "type": "string"
          }
        }
      }
    }
  }
}

 ```

The response includes:

- `status`: A string indicating the status of the request.

- `data.photos`: An array of strings representing the URLs of the orphan's photos.

