The endpoint allows you to create a new sponsorship with the specified details.

### Request Body

- orphan (string): The ID of the orphan to be sponsored.

- amount (number): The sponsorship amount.

- currency (string): The currency in which the sponsorship amount is provided.

- frequency (string): The frequency of the sponsorship payment.

- endDate (string): The end date of the sponsorship.


