request.description:
### API Request Description

This endpoint allows users to make a financial donation to the general fund of an orphanage.

#### Request Body

- `amount` (number): The amount of the donation.

- `orphanage` (string): The ID of the orphanage to which the donation is being made.


#### Response

The response will be in JSON format and will include the following fields:

- `status` (string): The status of the donation request.

- `message` (string): A message related to the donation request.

- `data` (object): An object containing the following fields:

    - `donationId` (string): The ID of the donation.

    - `checkoutUrl` (string): The URL for the donation checkout.


#### JSON Schema

``` json
{
  "type": "object",
  "properties": {
    "status": { "type": "string" },
    "message": { "type": "string" },
    "data": {
      "type": "object",
      "properties": {
        "donationId": { "type": "string" },
        "checkoutUrl": { "type": "string" }
      }
    }
  }
}

