### POST /api/orphanage/volunteer-requests

This endpoint is used to create a volunteer request for an orphanage.

#### Request Body

- raw (application/json)

    - description: Description of the volunteer request

    - requiredSkills: Skills required for the volunteer

    - requiredServiceType: Type of service required

    - maxVolunteers: Maximum number of volunteers needed


#### Response

The response will be in the form of a JSON schema:

``` json
{
  "type": "object",
  "properties": {
    "status": {
      "type": "string"
    },
    "message": {
      "type": "string"
    },
    "data": {
      "type": "object",
      "properties": {
        "request": {
          "type": "object",
          "properties": {
            "orphanage": {
              "type": "string"
            },
            "description": {
              "type": "string"
            },
            "requiredSkills": {
              "type": "string"
            },
            "requiredServiceType": {
              "type": "string"
